        <h1>LimeChat 2.8</h1>
        <ul>
          <li>Use Oniguruma instead of ICU regexp for stability.</li>
          <li>Fixed an unstable scroller problem with larger fonts.</li>
          <li>Avoid using the system socks proxy when socks is disabled in the system network preferences.</li>
          <li>Fixed minor bugs.</li>
        </ul>
